longBusinessSummary: Givot Olam Oil Exploration-Limited Partnership(1993) operates as an oil and gas exploration company in Israel. It primarily holds ownership in Meged oil field, which includes the Rosh Ha'Ayin lease I/11 covering an area of 243 square kilometers. The company was founded in 1993 and is based in Jerusalem, Israel.
